ALI D Official Website

BIOGRAPHY

Hailing from Setif, Ali D, whose real name is Ali DAMICHE, has quickly captured the hearts of Algerian rap fans. Born in 2003, he has managed to impose his unique style, a harmonious blend of Algeria's musical roots and modern hip-hop trends. With his powerful voice and imperatively lyrics, he has become one of the spearheads of a new generation of Algerian artists who are reinventing urban music.
